==Trivia==
*{{Wp|Bryophyta}} is the scientific name for mosses.
*The update which introduced Bryophyta also made [[Antipoison]] potions available to free-to-play players and able to be purchased from the [[Apothecary]] in Varrock.
**The idea of Bryophyta poisoning in free-to-play was scrapped prior to release; however, [[Antipoison]] potions still remain free-to-play.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1231689392995078146|date=23 February 2020|archiveurl=https://archive.is/dFZAb|archivedate=28 February 2020|quote=Not sure. The development of that particular boss was difficult, due to the dev being very inexperienced at the time, with Maz having to step in very late on to take over. The original dev may have enabled them on F2P for a reason that was later scrapped.}}

